Subject: Re: [T2] fuel shutoff valve

Hazet makes some clamps in three sizes for this and similar applications. 
See 'em at:

http://www.hazet.de/eng/hits/hits.htm

There's even a video of them in use!

I've used regular small needle nose vise grips for this purpose. Just don't 
tighten them any more than you need to.

